{
  "stem": "3382.7",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Finally, one went to, at least-- you know, to let water out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the other finally said, OK, that's enough, he says.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He unbuckled his revolver and gave me the shovel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And that moment I saw-- [LAUGHS] so I dug myself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] He says, everything now-- I dug about an hour, maybe more.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But then, everything what happened to us probably takes longer to tell.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Fight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he say, give me the shovel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I gave him the shovel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And this way, I took the shovel, this way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So he put his hand, you know, his right hand, you know, his right hand to shield himself and-- with the revolver.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I hit him right here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I saw how his part of hand, you know, hangs only-- It's a-- And that-- and he started, you know-- he just cries, whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I hit the revolver-- I, I grabbed his revolver.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I pulled to the other one, who started to look at me very surprised, and didn't shoot, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And then I said, you know, you idiot, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "You have to cock, you know, first of all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "So I cocked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I went-- [POINTS].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I didn't kill neither one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But I hit the other one twice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And I ran.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "There were, you know, fish ponds.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I slipped into a fish pond.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And the rain started.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And I run into forest, [NON-ENGLISH] Forest, got lost.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I circled it for several days, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Once, once-- I was deadly tired.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "I was deadly-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was wet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "All the time it was raining.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "It was-- and finally, I came up to a place near, near Mosty.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Because I decided I'm going back to Zapole.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I have their armaments.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
